# RcCheckbox

Welcome to my `RcCheckbox` component.

## Installation & Import

```bash
yarn add @ids-ts/rc-checkbox
```

```tsx
import { RcCheckbox } from '@ids-ts/rc-checkbox';
```

## Props API

| Prop | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `a11yFocus` | `boolean` | No | - |
| `assignInputRef` | `(c: HTMLInputElement | null) => void` | No | A function to get reference to input element. |
| `checked` | `boolean` | No | Specifies whether the checkbox is checked. |
| `defaultChecked` | `boolean` | No | Initial checked state (uncontrolled). |
| `disabled` | `boolean` | No | - |
| `indeterminate` | `boolean` | No | Specifies when type is checkbox and in a indeterminate state [-]. |
| `name` | `string` | No | a name assign to the checkbox input |
| `onBlur` | `React.FocusEventHandler<HTMLInputElement>` | No | Callback function that is fired when a Checkbox has been blurred. |
| `onChange` | `(e: { target: { checked: boolean; value: string } }) => void` | No | Called when the checkbox state changes. |
| `onClick` | `React.MouseEventHandler<HTMLInputElement>` | No | Callback function that is fired when a Checkbox has been clicked. |
| `onFocus` | `React.FocusEventHandler<HTMLInputElement>` | No | Callback function that is fired when a Checkbox has been focused. |
| `readOnly` | `boolean` | No | - |
| `tabIndex` | `number` | No | tab-index assign to the checkbox input. |
| `type` | `'checkbox' | 'radio'` | No | - |
| `validationMessage` | `string` | No | Validation Message. |
| `InlineValidationMessage` | `'error', 'warning', 'success', 'invalid', 'info...` | Yes | - |

<details>
<summary>Full TypeScript Interface</summary>

```typescript
export interface RcCheckboxProps
  extends Omit<ThemeableElement<'input'>, 'onChange'> {
  /**
   * A11yFocus flag.
   *
   * @default false
   */
  a11yFocus?: boolean;
  /** A function to get reference to input element. */
  assignInputRef?: (c: HTMLInputElement | null) => void;
  /** Specifies whether the checkbox is checked. */
  checked?: boolean;
  /**
   * Specifies the initial state: whether or not the checkbox is checked.
   *
   * @default false
   */
  defaultChecked?: boolean;
  /**
   * Disable the checkbox.
   *
   * @default false
   */
  disabled?: boolean;
  /** Specifies when type is checkbox and in a indeterminate state [-]. */
  indeterminate?: boolean;
  /** a name assign to the checkbox input */
  name?: string;
  /** Callback function that is fired when a Checkbox has been blurred. */
  onBlur?: React.FocusEventHandler<HTMLInputElement>;
  /** Callback function that is fired when a Checkbox has been checked. */
  onChange?: (
    /** a customized event */
    e: {
      /** a modify event target */
      target: {
        /** a event target check value */
        checked?: boolean;
      };
      /** a modify event target */
      stopPropagation?(): void;
      /** a modify event target */
      preventDefault?(): void;
    }
  ) => void;
  /** Callback function that is fired when a Checkbox has been clicked. */
  onClick?: React.MouseEventHandler<HTMLInputElement>;
  /** Callback function that is fired when a Checkbox has been focused. */
  onFocus?: React.FocusEventHandler<HTMLInputElement>;
  /**
   * Make checkbox read only.
   *
   * @default false
   */
  readOnly?: boolean;
  /** tab-index assign to the checkbox input. */
  tabIndex?: number;
  /**
   * Type of the Rc-Checkbox, can be checkbox or radio
   *
   * @default 'checkbox'
   */
  type?: 'checkbox' | 'radio';
  /** Validation Message. */
  validationMessage?: string;
  /**
   * Validation Type from InlineValidationMessage: 'error', 'warning', 'success', 'invalid', 'info', or ''
   *
   * @default ''
   */
  validationType?: InlineValidationType;
}
```

</details>

